No. D-2965. Supreme Court of the United States April 17, 2017.

In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF HOWARD TENG-HAO MEI.

Howard Teng-Hao Mei, of Bethesda, Maryland, is suspended from the practice *1621of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
